uce the power consumption compared to a network\nwith no power control approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2016 18:33:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2016 09:08:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
